💥 Buddy Blast (Official Signature Game) 🎮 Overview 

Buddy Blast Roblox Buddy AI ka Official Signature Game hoga. Yeh ek Multiplayer Co-op Puzzle Adventure game hai jisme teamwork sabse important hoga.

Golden Rule:

No Player Can Win Alone.

Game gadgets ya fighting par nahi, balki Communication, Observation aur Teamwork par based hoga.

🌍 Theme & Story 

Players normal log hain jo sirf ghoomne aaye the, lekin achanak ek dangerous facility ke andar phans jaate hain.

Har Chapter ki apni alag story hogi.

Har Chapter complete karne ke baad Story Book ka ek part milega.

Saare Story Books collect karne ke baad Final Master Story unlock hogi jisme poori asli kahani reveal hogi.

🎨 Theme & Art Style Semi-Realistic + Stylized Mix Har Chapter ki apni alag Theme Har Room ka apna Background Har Chapter ka alag Music Match start hone par Random Theme bhi choose ho sakti hai. 👥 Multiplayer 

3 Players Required

Har Player match shuru hone par ek Room choose karega:

⬅ Left Room

⬆ Center Room

➡ Right Room

Ek baar Room choose karne ke baad us match ke liye wahi path lock ho jayega.

Teenon ke Rooms connected honge lekin physically ek dusre ke paas nahi honge.

Glass, Window ya Camera ke through dekh sakte hain.

Communication bahut important hogi.

🏢 Room System 

Total Rooms = 30

Har Player sirf 10 Rooms complete karega.

Left Player → 10 Rooms

Center Player → 10 Rooms

Right Player → 10 Rooms

Har Room me:

5 Main Puzzles 3 Side Puzzles 

Difficulty dheere-dheere badhegi.

Har Chapter ke baad phir se 3 naye Doors choose karne ka option milega.

👹 Boss Room System 

Boss Room ka matlab sirf Fight nahi.

Boss Room = Highest Difficulty Room

Kabhi:

Puzzle Escape Robot Reactor AI Machine Team Coordination 

Har Chapter ka apna Boss hoga.

Har Chapter me 5 Mini Boss Events bhi honge.

Boss ke baad Secret Room unlock ho sakta hai.

Reward seedha nahi milega.

Players ko khud search karna padega.

🎒 Gadgets & Tools 

Game complete karne ke liye Gadgets zaruri nahi.

Gadgets sirf Extra Advantage denge.

Classes ke hisaab se Gadgets milenge.

Maximum Carry Limit = 3 Gadgets

Upgrade System nahi hoga.

Shop se kharide gaye Gadgets permanently unlock rahenge.

Har Mode me Option hoga:

✅ Gadgets ON

❌ Gadgets OFF

🤖 AI System 

Buddy sirf Help karega.

Hint de sakta hai.

Kabhi-kabhi Advice dega.

Communication karega.

Commentary nahi karega (sirf jab required ho).

Agar Player Disconnect ho jaye to Buddy AI temporary uski jagah aa sakta hai agar Team chahe.

📺 TV Support 

Game TV Browser par bhi chalega.

TV Remote se bhi playable hoga.

Controller Recommended hoga.

TV Players ke liye Special Quick Chat System hoga.

Microphone optional hoga.

